name: Rose J
description: I am a serious woman, who doesn’t want to play games with men. I came on this site for meeting my lovely man, who will be everything for me; my best friend, passionate lover and my soulmate. As for me, I have a strong character but also a kind heart. Furthermore, I know what the feeling of love is and how to make my beloved happy person! I am a real woman, smart and dreamy, affectionate and sincere, but sometimes strict and furious. I know what I want from life and will do all my best for this. I sincerely hope, that you find me an attractive woman for you and we can open a new page in our life.
